            <span class="section-tag">How It Works</span>
            <h2><span class="heading-bold">Up and running in minutes,</span><br><span class="heading-light">not months.</span></h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Fund-Raise replaces the patchwork of spreadsheets, email threads, and manual reports with one unified platform your entire team can trust.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-steps">
            <div class="hiw-step">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">1</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-connector"></div>
                <div class="hiw-step-icon blue">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="hiw-step-title">Upload your data</h3>
                <p class="hiw-step-desc">Import your department spreadsheets from Raiser's Edge or any source. Fund-Raise automatically parses gift types, funds, sources, and goals — no manual data entry.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">2</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-connector"></div>
                <div class="hiw-step-icon gold">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="hiw-step-title">See the full picture</h3>
                <p class="hiw-step-desc">Every department — Annual Giving, Major Gifts, Events, Direct Mail, and Legacy — on one dashboard. Compare progress, spot trends, and track against goals in real time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">3</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-icon navy">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
